<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>진료 완료 내역</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">진료 완료 내역</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">오늘 진료가 완료된 환자 목록입니다.</p>
            </div>
            
            <form action="/doctor/completed" method="GET" class="relative w-full md:w-64 ml-auto">
                <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="keyword"
                    value=""
                    placeholder="환자명 검색..."
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none text-sm"
                />
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-100 text-slate-400">
                            <i data-lucide="user" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-lg">박민수</h3>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
                                <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                                08:30
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-slate-200 text-slate-600">진료 완료</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-600 line-clamp-2 border border-slate-100">
                    급성 위염 의심. 위장약 처방.
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                    <button onclick="location.href='/doctor/record/1'" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-1">
                        <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-4 h-4"></i> 기록 보기
                    </button>
                    <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-purple-50 text-purple-600">전화</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="flex gap-2"><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded">1</span><a href="?page=2" class="px-3 py-1 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded">2</a></nav>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
